text:
The class org.apache.tools.zip.ZipOutputStream has a small error with the flush 
method.

Here's the patch that will correct it.

Regards,

Tamas serveny

--- ZipOutputStream.old	2004-02-12 13:33:36.000000000 +0000
+++ ZipOutputStream.java	2004-04-18 22:30:32.000000000 +0100
@@ -506,7 +506,7 @@
      * @since 1.14
      */
     public void flush() throws IOException {
-        if (out == null) {
+        if (out != null) {
             out.flush();
         }
     }
